RACE.FOOTNOTES: EARLY DAWN raced within contention, waited on the inside around the turn, got through on the inside entering the home stretch and drove clear. MOVE FORWARD ESSIE raced evenly near the back, finished wide and was never a threat. NATURALBORNSENDER raced in the middle of the field, saved ground and dropped back. EZ'S KOOL BREEZE broke a step slow, trailed the field and was distanced. PER RULING #25248 FROM THE LOUISIANA HORSE RACING COMMISSION EARLY DAWN WAS DQD FOR A POSITIVE TEST
